Loads the data from a CSV file.

Fixes date formats to enable proper time-based operations.

Removes invalid ages (e.g., negative or unrealistic ages over 120).

Converts the 'No_show' column into binary format (0 = showed up, 1 = no-show) for easier analysis.

Deletes rows with missing values to ensure data quality.

Adds a new 'WaitingDays' column, which calculates how long each patient waited for their appointment.

Saves the cleaned dataset to a new CSV file.

